/>\n但而家佢撤唔撤回都好，831太子站有冇死人、有冇極嚴重傷勢受害人，呢d都係要查啊！唔好俾佢轉移焦點啊！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好認真，點解一路發生咁多件事，都冇話撤回，突然今日會講起？到底呢幾日發生咗咩事逼到佢要做野？係咪真係其實死咗人？就算冇死人，到底情況係幾嚴重？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要求黨鐵交出831太子站完整CCTV記錄啊！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"10afe39eae4bfa0b230c9a08189e988679a4c75a","tid":1538962,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:52:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">六大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iHJFfmd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiHJFfmd.jpg&h=5166b6cf&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}